               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner's Defence.</hi> I was selling pies at the fair, and after I had sold them I was running about the fair—a lot more boys were playing—I ran round the show—a policeman came—he took me, and asked roe if I knew anything about a reticule—I said no, and he took me to the lady, who said she was quite certain I was the boy—I never saw the bag, the lady, or the child.</p>
